## Checkpoint table (after every step)

**Print once per step, after VERIFY. The VERIFY section is the annotated plan table — not a summary.**
**Protocol:** [`executor-protocol.mdc`](executor-protocol.mdc) — session startup, CONTRACT first, forbidden actions.

```markdown
### Checkpoint — Plan NNN Step X.Y
| Phase | Evidence |
|-------|----------|
| READ | [pre-state grep/Read outputs] |
| CONTRACT | [VERIFY table pasted verbatim from plan — pre-edit] |
| PROPOSE | [files + symbols] |
| TEST | [files touched] |
| VERIFY | See annotated table below |
| SELF-REVIEW | [§1b table — mandatory] |
| **Status** | BLOCKED | PARTIAL @ hash | SHIPPED |

| # | Claim | Command / Read | Pass when | Result |
|---|-------|----------------|-----------|--------|
| 1 | … | `rg …` | … | PASS (exit 0) |
| 2 | … | `npx vitest …` | … | FAIL (exit 1) → fixed in TEST, re-VERIFY |
```

SHIPPED only when every Result is PASS in **this** message **and** SELF-REVIEW row 1 is Yes.

**Self-review (required in checkpoint message):** See §1b — append the SELF-REVIEW table directly under the checkpoint before delivering.

**Forbidden until checkpoint shows all steps SHIPPED:**
- "Phase complete"
- "All tests green" (without per-step evidence)
- "Ready for next phase"
- SHIPPED with any Result showing FAIL

